Forest Act
Minimum Stumpage Rate Regulation
Minimum stumpage rate
1  The minimum stumpage rate for the purposes of section 105 (6) of the Forest Act is $0.25 a cubic metre.

Note: this regulation replaces B.C. Reg. 560/78.

[Provisions of the Forest Act, R.S.B.C. 1996, c. 157, relevant to the enactment of this regulation: section 105 (6)]
